Package net.opentsdb.uid

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    UniqueIdInterface Deprecated
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RandomUniqueId
    Generate Random UIDs to be used as unique ID.
    UniqueId
    Represents a table of Unique IDs, manages the lookup and creation of IDs.
    UniqueIdFilterPlugin
    A filter that can determine whether or not UIDs should be allowed assignment based on their metric and tags.
    UniqueIdWhitelistFilter
    A UID filter implementation using regular expression based whitelists.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    UniqueId.UniqueIdType
    Enumerator for different types of UIDS @since 2.0
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    FailedToAssignUniqueIdException
    Thrown when we failed to assign an ID to a string such as a metric, tagk or tag v.
    NoSuchUniqueId
    Exception used when a Unique ID can't be found.
    NoSuchUniqueName
    Exception used when a name's Unique ID can't be found.
